                "invention-title": [
                    "Device and method for preparing trichlorosilane through hydrogenation reduction of silicon tetrachloride",
                    "一种用于四氯化硅氢化还原制备三氯氢硅的装置及其方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of new energy photovoltaic silicon material preparation, and discloses a device and a method for preparing trichlorosilane through hydrogenation reduction of silicon tetrachloride. The device consists of a high-density rapid fluidized bed, a cyclone separation system, a material return system, a waste heat recovery system, a cooling system and a fractionating tower. Particles, separated by a primary cyclone separator, of a gas-solid mixture after reaction are returned to the turbulent flow fluidization section, particles separated by secondary or more cyclone separators are returned to the rapid fluidization section, separated crude product gas passes through a waste heat recovery system and a condensation system, separation of hydrogen and chlorosilane is achieved, and the chlorosilane is recycled. Liquid chlorosilane enters the fractionating tower to obtain trichlorosilane and silicon tetrachloride, and the light component trichlorosilane enters the reduction furnace to be used for preparing polycrystalline silicon. The method for preparing trichlorosilane through hydrogenation reduction of silicon tetrachloride has the advantages that gas-solid contact is sufficient, heat and mass transfer is rapid, the hydrogenation reaction conversion rate is higher, the reactor operation flexibility is large, and the volume utilization rate is high."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于新能源光伏硅材料制备技术领域，公开了一种用于四氯化硅氢化还原制备三氯氢硅的装置及其方法。该装置由高密度快速流化床、旋风分离系统、回料系统、余热回收系统系统、冷却系统以及分馏塔组成。反应后的气固混合物经一级旋风分离器分离的颗粒返回至湍流流化段，经二级及以上旋风分离器分离的颗粒返回至快速流化段，分离出来的粗产品气经余热回收系统和冷凝系统，实现氢气和氯硅烷的分离，而液态氯硅烷进入分馏塔中获得三氯氢硅和四氯化硅，其中轻组分三氯氢硅去还原炉用于制备多晶硅。该四氯化硅氢化还原制备三氯氢硅方法具有气固接触充分，传热和传质迅速，氢化反应转化率更高，反应器操作弹性大、体积利用率高的优点。"
                }
            ]
